{"tid":1224172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登讚香港示威者勇敢 警告支那「全世界都在看」","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T03:24:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"781dd91a6e4c7fa4141e9fd13a44e1aa1157930f","tid":1224172,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:21:12.000Z","msg":"中央社華盛頓14日綜合外電報導）前美國副總統、目前聲勢領先的民主黨總統參選人拜登（Joe Biden）今天推文聲援香港「反送中」修法抗議行動，同時提醒北京當局「全世界都在看」。<br />\n<br />\n香港本週發生1997年主權移交以來最嚴重的政治暴力事件，震撼這個全球金融中心。香港特首林鄭月娥面臨越來越大的壓力，要她放棄強行推動不得人心的逃犯條例修訂案。這項修訂案允許引渡人犯到中國。<br />\n<br />\n拜登今天推文說：「數百萬香港民眾為捍衛中國政府當初承諾的公民自由和自治權走上街頭，從中展現的非凡勇氣，激勵人心。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登在推文中還說：「全世界都在看&hellip;我們所有人必須挺身支持民主原則和自由。」"},{"pid":"e68bbd6fca25591d6fd6c0821bdc31b51bb8bd3c","tid":1224172,"uid":110351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:22:06.000Z","msg":"Creepy Joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c4e52b2a7c05dfb0e1f78f8411c8cbf3e65d54","tid":1224172,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a75f6bde61d1568e8e3746dccc8cdf62e4d506d","tid":1224172,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:22:26.000Z","msg":"ok副總統認證<br />\n<br />\ntrump專心做大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f0ca7512cd5c9bc857f939f000f7682152a624","tid":1224172,"uid":4206,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"8a75f6bde61d1568e8e3746dccc8cdf62e4d506d","tid":1224172,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:22:26.000Z","msg":"ok副總統認證<br />\n<br />\ntrump專心做大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"前副總統<br />\n而家嗰個係彭斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695c56298eff506cf6aae0ca22fde96c1ff8632a","tid":1224172,"uid":164442,"like":4,"disl